00:47:08,041 --> 00:47:10,601
And Yvonne goes to the university.

523
00:47:11,561 --> 00:47:23,760
And he's all of this, and particularly, I think going into philosophy and science, is something that shows that he's striving for some goal that they mostly can't understand.

