00:48:59,681 --> 00:49:02,481
But he doesn't say it quite that way here, he said.

539
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:10,921
But he does say at the bottom 76 that it's only because of religion and belief in immortality that people are good.

540
00:49:11,240 --> 00:49:18,521
If you destroy in mankind the belief in immortality, not only love but every living force maintaining the life of the world would be dried up.

