00:49:23,800 --> 00:49:30,121
And jumping ahead, Zosima says, Do you really believe that?

544
00:49:30,121 --> 00:49:31,400
The middle of.

545
00:49:32,360 --> 00:49:34,201
Is that really your conviction?

546
00:49:34,201 --> 00:49:36,441
A third of the way down on 77.

547
00:49:36,440 --> 00:49:41,800
As to the consequences of the disappearance of faith and immortality, Father Zima now asks Yvonne.

548
00:49:41,800 --> 00:49:43,401
Yes, that's my contention.

549
00:49:43,400 --> 00:49:46,361
There is no virtue if there's no immortality.

550
00:49:46,360 --> 00:49:49,720
You are blessed in believing that, or else most unhappy.

