00:49:59,961 --> 00:50:03,881
We have to discuss the article on church jurisdiction at a different later.

555
00:50:03,880 --> 00:50:10,601
Perhaps you were right, but I wasn't altogether joking, Yvonne suddenly and strangely confessed, blushing quickly.

556
00:50:10,601 --> 00:50:13,640
You were not altogether joking, that's true.

557
00:50:13,641 --> 00:50:15,480
The question is still bothering your heart.

558
00:50:15,481 --> 00:50:16,840
It is still unanswered.

559
00:50:16,840 --> 00:50:23,161
That the martyr sometimes likes to divert himself with his despair, as if driven to it by despair itself.

