00:50:23,161 --> 00:50:27,641
Meanwhile, in your despair, you too divert yourself.

561
00:50:28,280 --> 00:50:33,240
And they're still discussing this question of immortality.

562
00:50:33,561 --> 00:50:39,641
It's a question you have not answered, and this is your great grief, for it clamors for an answer.

563
00:50:40,201 --> 00:50:41,240
That's what Zosima says.

564
00:50:41,240 --> 00:50:49,321
But can it be answered by me, answered in the affirmative, Ivan went on, asking strangely, still looking at the elder with the same inexplicable smile.

