00:53:48,360 --> 00:53:53,240
And unless you get the earthly and the heavenly together, you haven't got it made.

611
00:53:53,561 --> 00:53:55,720
That's Dostoevsky's formulation of it.

612
00:53:55,720 --> 00:53:59,720
He has lots of formulations of it, but one of them is that way of thinking about it.

613
00:54:00,601 --> 00:54:10,361
And Sostima understands that, and he's trying to steer Ivan in this right direction of getting the earthly and heavenly together.

